com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded
Class AbstractCacheEngine

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.engine.Engine
      com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded.AbstractCacheEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Engine>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EhCacheEngine, ScheduledCacheEngine
public abstract class AbstractCacheEngine
extends Engine

This class is an abstraction of an engine which reads from a cache the nuts associated to a workflow to be processed. If an entry exists, then the nuts are returned and no more engine is executed. Otherwise, the chain is executed and the result is put in the cache.

The cache itself is abstract here and it needs to be provided by subclass.
